      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VERBOSITY (6) was having first run for the new yard when beaten a nose behind Black Zous, who is in the previous race. Fitter again and extra trip a plus. Plummets in the weights and can go one better. HEBEL (7) was about a length away from VERBOSITY last time in third. Worse off at the weights as the claimer is replaced by a senior rider this time. Will strip far fitter for it though and expected to feature again. ALTAR BOY (1) is a last start course and distance winner and will take catching off the low draw. THE GIRL'S BOY (3) strips fitter and expected to figure prominently.",
